<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>• ضعفه الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ. <span class="c2">«لسان الميزان»</span> ٥ <span class="c2">(٧١١٧)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
